-- Wilex Gets Mandatory Takeover Bid by Dievini Hopp BioTech at EU4.10/Share
-- Mike Gavin
-- 2010-07-15T08:52:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-15/wilex-gets-mandatory-takeover-bid-by-dievini-hopp-biotech-at-eu4-10-share.html

          
          
             Wilex AG said it received a tender
offer for a mandatory takeover bid by Dievini Hopp BioTech
Holding GmbH & Co. KG. The offer price is 4.10 euros per share,
exceeding the statutory minimum price of 4.07 euros, Wilex said.  
          
          


  


        